      "text": "We have gasoline.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We were going to-- to [INAUDIBLE], to the rabbi.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] Every time they saw girls with bellies, they were hiding in their rooms.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they didn't want to be a minyan.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They wanted to rest after work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they [LAUGHS] were hiding, locking up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Anyhow, our boys from our-- from our kibbutz, the young guys, were sitting there on the lawn.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They were waiting for the order to go to the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was-- they had the battles in the Jordan-- at Jordan, in the Jordan Valley.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Their [INAUDIBLE] didn't have the orders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So they were happy to have something to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There was on guy called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He was the clown of the group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He went the head of the procession and did ta, ta, ta-ra da, da, da.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "After that, I came with my belly after that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then [INAUDIBLE] kind of my husband's [INAUDIBLE] little shape [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Then came [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Ziva, ?] came with her belly and [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Eliezer ?] after her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We walked around the lawn, and we came down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we got a chuppah, and we were standing there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And the whistle blows.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And the [INAUDIBLE], and they jump on the track and went to the battle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And here we were standing there, the rabbi with a belly, [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Ziva ?] with a belly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I with a belly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Without a minyan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Now we had to call the guys, the people from the-- from the kibbutz to come out to make a minyan.",
